<li>📈 <a href="/scp-4809">SCP-4809</a> (&quot;Peeping Doesn't Pay&quot;) - Come on, this is ridiculous. I mean&#8230; a pic of naked Scarlett Johansson and people clicked on it without a doubt ? Really ? Yes, really. Written by Dr Astari.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/scp-4695">SCP-4695</a> (&quot;<span style="color: #e7cf00">S</span>y<span style="color: #0c00ff">n</span><span style="color: #ff0000">e</span><span style="color: #e7cf00">s</span><span style="color: #10af00">t</span><span style="color: #00d6d3">h</span><span style="color: #ff0000">e</span><span style="color: #e7cf00">s</span><span style="color: #78e7db">i</span><span style="color: #ff2d2d">a</span> <span style="color: #78e7db">I</span><span style="color: #0c00ff">n</span><span style="color: #2d40ff">d</span><span style="color: #8d47ff">u</span><span style="color: #068d00">c</span><span style="color: #ff0000">e</span><span style="color: #f818ff">r</span>&quot;) - Colors everywhere. Because black and white became more and more sad after all these years, don't you think ? Written by Lilac Snow.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-4386">SCP-4386</a> (&quot;B Gone, B&quot;) - I had a pro lem with my key oard so that's why this lur is written like that. Written y CyrusFiredawn.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-4609">SCP-4609</a> (&quot;An Object&quot;) - This is simple. You had an object, in one side. And in the other side, you had a suicidal researcher. Now, sit down and watch. Written by Tanhony.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-4258">SCP-4258</a> (&quot;Freddy's Diner&quot;) - &quot;<em>The inside of the restaurant is that of a stereotypical 50's American diner and is manned by a sole worker, an elderly Caucasian male who identifies as &quot;Freddy&quot;, otherwise known as SCP-4258-1.</em>&quot; Written by Malvarik1.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-4815">SCP-4815</a> (&quot;Busted Oracle&quot;) - You're overreacting, he's not so broken. A little bit of Scranton Reality Glue and it will be like new. Written by faminepulse.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/scp-4771">SCP-4771</a> (&quot;Kurentovanje&quot;) - <span style="color: blue">How do you do ?</span> Written by LifeBot.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-4278">SCP-4278</a> (&quot;The Island at the End&quot;) - &quot;<em>Everyone I know. Goes in an island. In the end.</em>&quot; Written by Tanhony.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-4354">SCP-4354</a> (&quot;From The Ink Under Your Skin To Flesh&quot;) - It's not so difficult to wrote with that. Written by Crashington.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/scp-4308">SCP-4308</a> (&quot;Heartfelt&quot;) - &quot;<em>Yeah, Duke was really talented. The song 'Overshadowed,' that's the one that had all the weird stuff.</em>&quot; Written by DianaBerry.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc6"><span>Tales</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>📈 <a href="/apologies-and-redemption">Apologies and Redemption</a> - &quot;<em>I said I'm sorry. On behalf of the Foundation, I want to apologize to you. You're right. We could have done better. We should have done better.</em>&quot; Written by DrMorris.</li>
